学手段进行证明的交易理论。\n</pre>\n<p>看了网上关于缠论的讨论非常多，很多人声称学了反而亏钱了，看起来缠论也比较难学。</p>\n<p>有没有大佬亲身经历实战证明。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1627062997, "replies": 28, "id": 791443}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f749/09ac/430_large.png?m=1347578950", "name": "icloud", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f749/09ac/430_normal.png?m=1347578950", "title": "iCloud", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/icloud", "topics": 644, "footer": null, "header": "Store contacts, calendars, photos, music, books, apps and more in the cloud and access them on all your devices.", "title_alternative": "iCloud", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f749/09ac/430_mini.png?m=1347578950", "stars": 151, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 430, "parent_node_name": "apple"}, "member": {"username": "Brrrr", "website": "", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b826/3d4b/439703_mini.png?m=1588991731", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Brrrr", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1567588690, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b826/3d4b/439703_mini.png?m=1588991731", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b826/3d4b/439703_mini.png?m=1588991731", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 439703}, "last_reply_by": "littlewing", "last_touched": 1627135302, "title": "2T 的 iCloud 家庭共享满了怎么办", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/791462", "created": 1627089718, "content": "RT<br>国区 2T 的 iCloud 空间满了，家里几个人自用的，有什么办法？求高手", "content_rendered": "<p>RT<br/>国区 2T 的 iCloud 空间满了，家里几个人自用的，有什么办法？求高手</p>\n", "last_modified": 1627089718, "replies": 26, "id": 791462}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1620107025", "name": "bb", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1620107025", "title": "宽带症候群", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb", "topics": 9585, "footer": "", "header": "网速很重要。比快更快。", "title_alternative": "Broadband Symptom Complex", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/